entry.title: Tabu Beats Up Satish Kaushik - Comedy Scene - Saajan Chale Sasural
entry.content: Watch the hindi comedy scene from the bollywood superhit romantic comedy blockbuster hindi movie Saajan Chale Sasural (1996) whereMutthuswami (Satish Kaushik) is beaten by Divya Khurana (Tabu) as he tries to steal her purse. Continue watching to know more. The film stars bollywood actors Govinda, Karishma Kapoor, Tabu, Satish Kaushik, Shakti Kapoor & Kader Khan. Directed by David Dhawan & Produced by Mansoor Siddique. Music by Nadeem Shravan.

entry.title: Sanjeev Kumar Twin Brother Confusion Comedy Scene -- Angoor
entry.content: Watch the hit comedy scene from the bollywood classic romantic comedy hindi movie Angoor (1982) starring Sanjeev Kumar, Maushmi Chatterjee, Deven Verma, Shammi & Utpal Dutt. Directed by Gulzar & Produced by Jai Singh. Music by R.D Burman. The film is about two pairs of identical twins separated at birth and how their lives go haywire when they meet in adulthood.
